---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="关于 - Fine"
  description="关于 Fine：聚焦 AI 与软件工程实践，记录技术栈、写作方向与协作方式。"
  tags={['关于作者', 'AI 工程', '软件开发']}
  schemaType="AboutPage"
  schemaTitle="关于 Fine"
>
  <article class="about">
    <h1>关于我</h1>
    <p class="tagline">
      <span class="highlight">Vibe Coding Engineer</span> · 在 AI 浪潮中寻找人机协作的最佳节奏
    </p>
    <p>
      这个博客是我记录学习历程、分享技术心得的地方。写作是最好的学习方式之一，
      通过整理和输出知识，能够加深对技术的理解。
    </p>
    
    <h2>技术栈</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>前端：TypeScript, React, Vue, Astro</li>
      <li>后端：Node.js, Python, Go</li>
      <li>数据库：PostgreSQL, MongoDB, Redis</li>
      <li>DevOps：Docker, Kubernetes, CI/CD</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>联系方式</h2>
    <p>
      如果你有任何问题或想法，欢迎通过以下方式联系我：
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/fine405" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@fine405</a></li>
      <li>Email: 18224017933@163.com</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>博客特性</h2>
    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature">
        <span class="icon">🚀</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Astro 驱动</h3>
          <p>基于 Astro 构建，静态生成带来极致性能</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <span class="icon">🏷️</span>
        <div>
          <h3>标签分类</h3>
          <p>文章按标签归类，快速找到感兴趣的内容</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <span class="icon">📅</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Git 时间追踪</h3>
          <p>自动从 Git 提交记录获取发布和更新时间</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <span class="icon">🖼️</span>
        <div>
          <h3>图片灯箱</h3>
          <p>点击图片全屏预览，支持左右导航浏览</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <span class="icon">📡</span>
        <div>
          <h3>RSS 订阅</h3>
          <p>支持 RSS Feed，用你喜欢的阅读器订阅</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <span class="icon">🔍</span>
        <div>
          <h3>SEO 优化</h3>
          <p>完善的 Open Graph 和结构化数据支持</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <span class="icon">💬</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Giscus 评论</h3>
          <p>基于 GitHub Discussions 的评论系统</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <span class="icon">🌓</span>
        <div>
          <h3>主题切换</h3>
          <p>支持亮色/暗色主题，自动跟随系统偏好</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .about p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .tagline .highlight {
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      #667eea,
      #764ba2,
      #f093fb,
      #667eea
    );
    background-size: 300% 300%;
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    font-weight: 600;
    animation: gradient-shift 8s ease infinite;
  }

  @keyframes gradient-shift {
    0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
    100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
  }

  .about ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .about li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .feature {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  .feature:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .feature .icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .feature h3 {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .feature p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
</style>
